text:
Things have gone from mediocre to worse.  Just a few highlights:

. internet and phone down for DAYS with no sense of urgency to fix;
. no compensation for payments made for same services they not provided;
. month and month of billing problems / they can't get their accounting straight;
. poor user interface on the account side / you can't actually manage your account;
. they are making it harder and harder to communicate with the office team;
. understaffed for months resulting in many client calls going direct to voicemail;
. nothing but lip service from senior management from valid complaints;

If we were not already established here with a business address we would leave.  Highly recommend looking elsewhere.
